          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "'Authors comment'",
                "I-126 can be formed via two routes,namely Xe-126(n,p)",
                "and the depletion of I-125 via I-125(n,g) during the",
                "irradiation. The relative proportion of I-126 formed",
                "via I-125(n,g) turned out to be much higher than that",
                "via Xe-126(n,p).",
                "The cross-section measurement of the Xe-126(n,p)I-126",
                "reaction would therefore contain a relatively large",
                "error."
              ]
            }
